001/03/01/bw/0000-0516-ca-iso

MISSOURI POWER GENERATION STATION SALE ANNOUNCED
Duke Energy North America today announced the sale of its 100-percent 
interest in a 640-megawatt power plant under construction in Audrain County, 
Mo., to NRG Energy Inc. for an undisclosed sum.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMANAT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/comtex/2
001/03/01/pr/0000-2512-.industrytopstories.util

RG&E RESTRUCTURES TO PROMOTE NATURAL-GAS COMPETITION
The New York Public Service Commission has approved a plan to restructure an 
upstate utility's natural-gas operations in an effort to promote retail 
competition.
